382
00:34:44,479 --> 00:34:45,800
A terrible brother indeed.

383
00:34:53,599 --> 00:34:58,200
If I had known the truth
three years ago,

384
00:34:59,399 --> 00:35:00,472
and chosen to run away,

385
00:35:02,359 --> 00:35:03,448
