386
00:35:16,519 --> 00:35:17,528
You wouldn't.

387
00:35:24,119 --> 00:35:25,119
Actually, I really wish I had.

388
00:35:29,960 --> 00:35:32,040
But there are things
that I must do myself.

389
00:35:34,560 --> 00:35:35,640
Moreover,

390
00:35:37,479 --> 00:35:39,639
